{
  "name": "RPlog_Corellian_Slave_Liberation",
  "title": "Corellian Slave Liberation",
  "summary": "A New Republic strike team disguised as animal-control workers infiltrates Coronet spaceport to free drugged slaves being loaded aboard an Imperial freighter bound for Kessel. When the ISB agent Marx grows suspicious and drags the defector Galatea off as a hostage, Commander Stail's team springs the trap early with tear gas and grenades, while Marine Captain Vengan storms the security building to rescue her. A chaotic firefight erupts as ISB and COMPNOR troops, then a fresh squad of Stormtroopers led by the commando Sig and the medic TK-4463, pour in to contain the raid. The rebels seize the freighter and crack open the crates, but Shael is gunned down and left behind alongside four captives, while Vengan and Galatea, deafened and cornered, blow open a sewage pipe and escape into the drains. The captured freighter blasts into space pursued by Liza Molokai's TIEs and an assault shuttle, but pilot Cherlin shakes the tractor beam and jumps to hyperspace, escaping with the freed slaves while the Imperials are left empty-handed.",
